Class OperatorCountry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team6.project.entities.OperatorCountry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class OperatorCountry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class creates an Entity called OperatorCountry which implements Serializable and uses the composite key called OperatorCountryPK.

    It creates 3 columns called mcc , mnc , country and operator
